{"tid":1256484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】李飛：不理解為何有人以暴力方式反對政府","createTime":"2019-06-25T04:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T06:03:43.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"51914526a055eff0c9a486e2f0d7afeec7db3f59","tid":1256484,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【逃犯條例】李飛：不理解為何有人以暴力方式反對政府</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n港府提出修訂《逃犯條例》，引發多場示威衝突。在北京，全國人大憲法和法律委員會主任李飛表示，不理解香港為何有人以暴力違法方式反對政府。<br />\n<br />\n李飛稱，香港是一個法治地方，可以和平集會遊行表達訴求，但不可理解為何每次反對政府示威都有暴力，「你不管怎樣擔心，不能違法，你對警察採取了措施，這種傷害的辦法」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190625/s00001/1561431207712/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e6%9d%8e%e9%a3%9b-%e4%b8%8d%e7%90%86%e8%a7%a3%e7%82%ba%e4%bd%95%e6%9c%89%e4%ba%ba%e4%bb%a5%e6%9a%b4%e5%8a%9b%e6%96%b9%e5%bc%8f%e5%8f%8d%e5%b0%8d%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190625%2Fs00001%2F1561431207712%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%259d%258e%25e9%25a3%259b-%25e4%25b8%258d%25e7%2590%2586%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e7%2582%25ba%25e4%25bd%2595%25e6%259c%2589%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e6%259a%25b4%25e5%258a%259b%25e6%2596%25b9%25e5%25bc%258f%25e5%258f%258d%25e5%25b0%258d%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%25ba%259c&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443tHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=19e57644\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190625%2Fs00001%2F1561431207712%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%259d%258e%25e9%25a3%259b-%25e4%25b8%258d%25e7%2590%2586%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e7%2582%25ba%25e4%25bd%2595%25e6%259c%2589%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e6%259a%25b4%25e5%258a%259b%25e6%2596%2